OL,3,CMan arrested following death of woman
OL,4,Cin her 60s
OL,6,FA 32-year-old man has been arrested on
OL,7,Fsuspicion of murder following the
OL,8,Fdeath of a woman in Whitfield near
OL,9,FDover.
OL,11,FKent Police was called to an address
OL,12,Fin Khartoum Square at 3.27pm on Sunday
OL,13,F29 March 2026, where a woman was being
OL,14,Ftreated by paramedics.
OL,16,FThe victim, who was in her 60s, died
OL,17,Fat the scene. Her next of kin have
OL,18,Fbeen informed.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/3
