OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1774966279
OL,3,CMan arrested following death of woman
OL,4,Cin her 60s
OL,6,FDetectives launched a murder
OL,7,Finvestigation and a man, who was known
OL,8,Fto the woman, was arrested on
OL,9,Fsuspicion of murder and taken into
OL,10,Fcustody.
OL,12,FA cordon remains at the property while
OL,13,Fenquiries into the incident are
OL,14,Funderway.JAnyone with information that
OL,15,Fmay assist the investigation should
OL,16,Fcall 01843 222289 quoting reference 29-
OL,17,F0827.
